OL,3,C#50,000 reward offered in unsolved
OL,4,Cmurder of Nottingham taxi driver
OL,6,FA reward of up to #50,000 is being
OL,7,Foffered from Crimestoppers as
OL,8,Fdetectives are re-investigating the
OL,9,Fmurder of a taxi driver in Nottingham.
OL,11,FEthsham Ul-Haq Ghafoor, 26, of
OL,12,FSherwood Rise, known to his friends
OL,13,Fand family as Shami, was shot dead in
OL,14,Fhis taxi on Tuesday 22 November 1994.
OL,16,FHe was found by a milkman at 4.30am at
OL,17,FLambley Lane Playing Fields in Gedling
OL,18,Fwith his hands tied and bound to the
OL,19,Fsteering wheel. He had been shot in
OL,20,Fwhat has been described by police as
OL,21,F"an execution."
