OL,6,FAssistant Chief Constable Rob Griffin
OL,7,Fsaid: "This was a dreadful murder of a
OL,8,Fyoung man, a soon-to-be-dad, who was
OL,9,Fexecuted in his own taxi in a secluded
OL,10,Farea of Nottinghamshire.
OL,12,F"At the heart of this horrific crime
OL,13,Fis a family; a family that have waited
OL,14,F30 years for answers, 30 years for
OL,15,Fjustice, 30 years for the closure they
OL,16,Frightfully deserve.
OL,18,F"Shami's mum never got that closure.
OL,19,FShe died never knowing why her eldest
OL,20,Fson's life was taken so cruelly from
OL,21,Fher.
OL,26,@oD@GOUtD@AOUzD@AOU
