OL,6,F"Shami's daughter was born without a
OL,7,Fdad, forced to live with other
OL,8,Fpeople's anecdotes of him, never
OL,9,Fhaving any of her own.
OL,11,F"Shami's brothers and sisters, who
OL,12,Fhave shown immense bravery and are
OL,13,Fsupporting our appeal, live with the
OL,14,Fpain and loss of their brother's death
OL,15,Fevery day.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
