OL,4,Cmurder of Nottingham taxi driver
OL,6,F"We stand beside them and want exactly
OL,7,Fthe same ` to ensure those who took
OL,8,Fhis life are found and put behind
OL,9,Fbars. I would ask the community to do
OL,10,Fthe same. To put themselves in Shami's
OL,11,Ffamily's shoes.
OL,13,F"Shami's family can never move on with
OL,14,Ftheir lives without answers and you
OL,15,Fcould be sitting on the very answers
OL,16,Fthey require.
OL,18,F"We know that there will be people out
OL,19,Fthere that know what happened, that
OL,20,Fhave that information.
