OL,6,F"Now is the time to act, to pick up
OL,7,Fthe phone, anonymously, if need be,
OL,8,Fand provide us with information.
OL,10,F"Crimestoppers is offering up to
OL,11,F#50,000 reward as an extra incentive.
OL,12,FThis is a huge reward for information
OL,13,Fthat leads to conviction. I would like
OL,14,Fto personally thank Crimestoppers for
OL,15,Ftheir help and wanting to support us
OL,16,Fin ensuring justice is served.
