OL,4,Cmurder of Nottingham taxi driver
OL,6,F"While a number of reviews of this
OL,7,Fterrible crime have been carried out
OL,8,Fover the last 30 years, unfortunately
OL,9,Fhis killer or killers have never been
OL,10,Fcaught.
OL,12,F"We have been working closely with
OL,13,FShami's family over the last 18
OL,14,Fmonths, during which time I have
OL,15,Fpersonally met with them several
OL,16,Ftimes. I have explained to them why we
OL,17,Fhave put together a new team of senior
OL,18,Fdetectives, a fresh pair of eyes, to
OL,19,Fensure that no stone is left unturned
OL,20,Fand that all new and existing avenues
OL,21,Fare explored.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
