OL,6,F"We are now calling on the community
OL,7,Ffor their help and assistance to
OL,8,Fensure that this crime does not go
OL,9,Funsolved."
OL,11,FShami had been working as a taxi
OL,12,Fdriver in the city on the night he was
OL,13,Fkilled and was well-known among his
OL,14,Fcolleagues.
OL,16,FThe last known sighting of Shami was
OL,17,Fat 2.40am in Carlton Square where he
OL,18,Fwas seen with three Asian men in his
OL,19,Fblack and white Ford Sierra.
