OL,6,FThe location his body was found was
OL,7,Fsecluded especially at night and not a
OL,8,Flocation usually used for taxi pick-
OL,9,Fups or drop-offs. The weapon used to
OL,10,Ftake his life has never been recovered.
OL,12,FHowever, due to major developments in
OL,13,Fforensic science, a number of items
OL,14,Fhave been examined from the scene of
OL,15,Fthe crime which is providing
OL,16,Fdetectives with new opportunities.
OL,18,FA number of people were arrested at
OL,19,Fthe time of Shami's murder, but no one
OL,20,Fhas ever been convicted of this
OL,21,Fhorrific crime.
