OL,6,F"We know it can be difficult for some
OL,7,Fpeople to speak directly to the police
OL,8,Fwhich is why our charity is here for
OL,9,Fyou.
OL,11,F"We are hoping that with the passage
OL,12,Fof time it will be easier to share
OL,13,Fwhat you know. We've been passing on
OL,14,Finformation about crime whilst
OL,15,Fguaranteeing anonymity since we were
OL,16,Festablished decades ago. It's a
OL,17,Fpromise we've always kept.
