OL,6,F"Crimestoppers is completely
OL,7,Findependent of the police. You can
OL,8,Fmake a difference by passing on what
OL,9,Fyou know whilst being protected by our
OL,10,Fguarantee of anonymity.
OL,12,F"That means no police, no courts, no
OL,13,Fwitness statements. Put simply, when
OL,14,Fyou contact our charity online or on
OL,15,Fthe phone, there's no comeback.
OL,17,F"We are open 24 hours a day, seven
OL,18,Fdays a week, 365 days a year. We
OL,19,Fcannot trace your call or track your
OL,20,FIP address.
